title: CDFW Receives Prestigious Award for Endangered Species Conservation (California Department of Fish and Wildlife)
text: ( Source : California Department of Fish and Wildlife ) The California Department of Fish and Wildlife (CDFW) and partners from government, education and private industry are being recognized for outstanding efforts in wildlife conservation.
